OL,3,CShoplifters feel they can rob with
OL,4,Cimpunity, Sussex police chief says
OL,6,FThe Police and Crime Commissioner for
OL,7,FSussex says some shoplifters "feel
OL,8,Fthey can rob shops with impunity."
OL,10,FKaty Bourne, the national lead for
OL,11,Fshoplifting at the Association of
OL,12,FPolice and Crime Commissioners, said
OL,13,Fmore robust police interventions and
OL,14,F"meaningful criminal justice measures"
OL,15,Fare needed to prevent reoffending.
OL,17,FShoplifting hit a record high in 2024,
OL,18,Fwith the number of offences surpassing
OL,19,F500,000 for the first time, up 20%
OL,20,Ffrom 2023.
