OL,3,CShoplifters feel they can rob with
OL,4,Cimpunity, Sussex police chief says
OL,6,FWriting in the Telegraph on Saturday,
OL,7,Fthe police and crime commissioner for
OL,8,FSussex said: "What on earth has
OL,9,Fhappened to our high streets and our
OL,10,Fcity centres? Why do some people feel
OL,11,Fthey can rob shops with impunity and
OL,12,Fabuse and assault staff without any
OL,13,Ffear of retribution?"
OL,15,FThere must be rehabilitation for some
OL,16,Foffenders as well as "significant
OL,17,Falternatives to our overcrowded
OL,18,Fprisons", she said.
