OL,3,CShoplifters feel they can rob with
OL,4,Cimpunity, Sussex police chief says
OL,6,FSussex will see "the first electronic
OL,7,Ftagging scheme for persistent
OL,8,Fshoplifters", Ms Bourne said.
OL,10,FThe force will work with the courts on
OL,11,Fhow to issue the tags and with
OL,12,Findustries to see how they can be
OL,13,Fmonitored.
OL,15,FThe policing chief also criticised the
OL,16,F"purist application of data protection
OL,17,Flaw" advising shopkeepers not to share
OL,18,Fimages of suspected offenders.
