OL,3,CShoplifters feel they can rob with
OL,4,Cimpunity, Sussex police chief says
OL,6,FJon Cummins, Assistant Chief Constable
OL,7,Ffrom Avon and Somerset Police, told
OL,8,FBBC Radio 4's Today programme that
OL,9,Fwider societal issues including
OL,10,Fpoverty, the cost-of-living crisis and
OL,11,Faddiction are contributing to the
OL,12,Fshoplifting spike.
OL,14,FHe said on Saturday: "If they see
OL,15,Fsomebody shoplifting, my advice to
OL,16,Fthem is they must call us ... not to
OL,17,Fintervene.
OL,19,F"We clearly want to be attending and
OL,20,Fwill be attending reports".
